The paper deals with face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves deep learning models, which falls under machine learning (cs.MM) and deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the challenges of low resolution face recognition, which could fall under computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
